{"tid":2383993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良: 紅磡粥店多人確診現警號","createTime":"2021-01-28T09:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T09:44:58.000Z","uid":102424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b46ff1e7e2c6a13fd3bb627b6c7afd7f9d03b50f","tid":2383993,"uid":102424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"紅磡指定區域有粥店多人確診。港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良認為，收緊防疫措施後仍然出現零星群組是一個警號，擔心會再出現社區爆發，政府應盡快完成群組追蹤。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良：「涉及食店至少有六宗確診及一宗初步確診，即傳播在那裡，不是這一兩日發生，可能早一星期之前已有傳播鏈，至現在至少傳了一代。這一小群組，隨時在該區又引發另一次較嚴重社區爆發，社區爆發才封區、封樓或突撃，不是好的策略，是少少「補鑊」的策略。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%95%E6%A0%A2%E8%89%AF-%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E7%B2%A5%E5%BA%97%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%8F%BE%E8%AD%A6%E8%99%9F-061239869.html?ncid=facebook_httpshkmob_mohvzzakd4a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%25A0%25A2%25E8%2589%25AF-%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%25A3%25A1%25E7%25B2%25A5%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%2599%259F-061239869.html%3Fncid%3Dfacebook_httpshkmob_mohvzzakd4a&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cUzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=e2900069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BD%95%E6%A0%A2%E8%89%AF-%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E7%B2%A5%E5%BA%97%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%8F%BE%E8%AD%A6%E8%99%9F-061239869.html?ncid=facebook_httpshkmob_mohvzzakd4a</a>"},{"pid":"320672f3f8362dbbce9311ec0b81a3ddaa1349fa","tid":2383993,"uid":102424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:30:07.000Z","msg":"睇落似又想不停封區封區封區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ea189df51fb3907e304b8c8023e008a298633e","tid":2383993,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"黃埔gg <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ec49b486c3085862e8c2a2694c00d747b